title: Miami-FSU tee it up; NW-Michigan, Cal-Utah in league games
text: > Top News Miami-FSU tee it up; NW-Michigan, Cal-Utah in league games FILE - In this Sept. 12, 2015, file photo, Florida State's Roberto Aguayo kicks an extra point from the hold of Cason Beatty during an NCAA college football game against South Florida in Tallahassee, Fla. New coaches, new players, new era, but Miami (3-1) and Florida State (4-0) tee it up again on Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, with Florida State looking to make it five wins in a row over Miami. (AP Photo/Steve Cannon, File)
